      <base_question>Next, you will be asked questions about your emotional state.       <sub_questions>

        <sub_question id="Unable to Control Important Things">how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Nervous and Stressed">how often have you felt nervous and stressed?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Lacked Confidence Handling Problems">how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Things Going Your Way">how often have you felt that things were going your way?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Unable to Cope">how often have you found that you could not cope with all the things that you had to do?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Irritated by Life">how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="On Top of Things">how often have you felt that you were on top of things?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Angered by Uncontrollable Events">how often have you been angered because of things that happened that were outside of your control?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Felt Overwhelmed">how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?</sub_question>

      <base_question>Next, you will be asked questions about your emotional state.       <sub_questions>
        <sub_question id="Upset by Unexpected Events">how often have you been upset because of something that happened unexpectedly?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Unable to Control Important Things">how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Nervous and Stressed">how often have you felt nervous and stressed?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Lacked Confidence Handling Problems">how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Things Going Your Way">how often have you felt that things were going your way?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Unable to Cope">how often have you found that you could not cope with all the things that you had to do?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Irritated by Life">how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="On Top of Things">how often have you felt that you were on top of things?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Angered by Uncontrollable Events">how often have you been angered because of things that happened that were outside of your control?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Felt Overwhelmed">how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?</sub_question>
      </sub_questions>
    </question>

    <question id="Emotional Regulation Frequency">
      <base_question>Next, you will be asked questions about your emotional state. Please answer on a scale of 0 to 4, where 0 is never, 1 is 'almost never', 2 is 'sometimes', 3 is 'fairly often', and 4 is 'very often', how often you experienced the following feelings during the last month: [Likert 0–4]</base_question>
      <sub_questions>
        <sub_question id="Upset by Unexpected Events">how often have you been upset because of something that happened unexpectedly?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Unable to Control Important Things">how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Nervous and Stressed">how often have you felt nervous and stressed?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Lacked Confidence Handling Problems">how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Things Going Your Way">how often have you felt that things were going your way?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Unable to Cope">how often have you found that you could not cope with all the things that you had to do?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Irritated by Life">how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="On Top of Things">how often have you felt that you were on top of things?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Angered by Uncontrollable Events">how often have you been angered because of things that happened that were outside of your control?</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Felt Overwhelmed">how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?</sub_question>
      </sub_questions>
    </question>
    <question id="Anxiety Symptoms Frequency">
      <base_question>Next, you will be asked questions about your emotional state. Please answer on a scale of 0 to 3, where 0 is 'Not at all', 1 is 'several days', 2 is 'more than half of the days', and 3 is 'Nearly every day'. Over the last two weeks, how often have you been bothered by the following problems? [Likert 0–3]</base_question>
      <sub_questions>
        <sub_question id="Feeling Nervous or On Edge">Feeling nervous, anxious, or on edge</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Uncontrollable Worrying">Not being able to stop or control worrying</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Excessive Worry">Worrying too much about different things</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Trouble Relaxing">Trouble relaxing</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Restlessness">Being so restless that it is hard to sit still</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Irritability">Becoming easily annoyed or irritable</sub_question>
        <sub_question id="Fear Something Awful Might Happen">Feeling afraid, as if something awful might happen</sub_question>

    </question>
